law.history: Repealed 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 70, sec. 31. -- Amended 1956 (2d Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 9, sec. 1. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 191, sec. 9.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Credit for taxes paid on fuel used in vehicles operated on highways of both this and other states; deferred credits.
